    "course_title": "LIE ALGEBRAS",
    "description": "Lie algebras and matrix groups. Topics: tangent spaces; exponentials; Baker-Campbell-Hausdorff formula; (nilpotent, solvable, semisimple) Lie algebras; Engel's and Lie's theorems; Levi decomposition; Killing form; sl(2)-representations; root systems; Dynkin diagrams; Weyl groups; Cartan and Borel subalgebras; Serre's theorem. Basic graduate algebra courses (e.g.MATH\u00a0541and542orMATH\u00a0741and742) are strongly recommended.",
